summary.en: Accentuated with a wrap design and tie-up detail, this vest is a stylish addition to your wardrobe. Tailored from cotton blend fabric, this sleeves vest can be teamed with a wide range of tops and dresses. The neutral tone makes it easily blend in with most of your outfits.
